  "body": "### Component\n\nAnvil\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nGanache v7 supports an RPC request called evm_setTime which allows the developer to set an arbitrary timestamp for the next block (even if that time is before the current blocktime). This can be useful for testing, since each transaction moves the clock to the current time turning the clock back isn't possible after a single transaction.\r\n\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
